dct_title_s: A topographical map of the vicinity of Trenton, New Brunswick and Bordentown
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From original surveys and levelings based on the triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey." In upper margin: Geological Survey of New Jersey. Atlas sheet no. 8 (Trenton). Originally issued folded in covers 24 x 17 cm.
dct_publisher_sm: [Trenton] : Geological Survey of New Jersey, 1887 ([New York] : Julius Bien & Co. Lith.)
